description.displayText: Amanda babysat our 5-month old son, giving Mom & Dad a few much needed date nights out.  She was great with him even when he was sick with an ear infection.  We felt comfortable with her in our home, and were very sad to see her move out of our zip code.  She always showed up up on time and was very flexible with us which was appreciated as two working parents with unpredictable schedules.
